$ System.Text.UTF8Encoding (class)

`System.Text.UTF8Encoding` derives from → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Text/Encoding[`System.Text.Encoding`].

{ Create an encoding with/without a BOM

  In order to create an → development/Unicode/UTF-8 encoding without a → development/Unicode/BOM, set the first parameter of the constructor to false.

}

